description: Bringing Poutines, Jerk Chicken wraps and awesome healthy choice food along with devilish Tempura Oreo's. Our Chefs Luv to create your eating pleasures!Lola D’s kitchen is a mobile catering business founded by friend’s looking for a way to share great healthy recipes to the Las Vegas community.   Lola D’s offers healthy food options for anyone wanting to eat well on-the-go.   Our menu consists of healthy, homemade cuisine created by our well seasoned chefs and characters, Lola and D.   Our goal as a mobile catering company is to provide a restaurant style experience with a variety of themed healthy hearty food’s from several mobile food trailers throughout Las Vegas and surrounding cities.
name: Lola D's Kitchen
